 Values for data0 and data1 for each button pressed:
 Button            Value    Variable
Square             0x7f     data1
Circle             0xdf     data1
Triangle           0xef     data1
Cross              0xbf     data1
Dpad Up            0xef     data0
Dpad Down          0xbf     data0
Dpad Left          0x7f     data0
Dpad Right         0xdf     data0
Analog Stick L     0xfd     data0
Analog Stick R     0xfb     data0
L1                 0xfb     data1
L2                 0xfe     data1
R1                 0xf7     data1
R2                 0xfd     data1
Start              0xf7     data0
Select             0xfe     data0

For the analog sticks(values between 0 and 0xff):
Left Stick: X axis - data4, Y axis - data5
Right Stick: X axis - data2, Y axis - data3


Control scheme for the arm servos:
Servo 1: Dpad Left and Dpad Right
Servo 2: Dpad Up and Dpad Down
Servo 3: Cross and Triangle
Servo 4: Square and Circle
Servo 5: L2 and R2
Servo 6: L1 and R1

-First servo is at the base of the arm
-Last servo opens and closes the claw